<DATELINE>
   SEOUL
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
South Korea wants the United Nations to give North Korea a deadline by which
it must open its nuclear sites to international inspection or be slapped
with economic sanctions, Seoul officials said yesterday, Reuter reports from
Seoul.
